# Sweet Provider

The "sweet" provider allows the interaction with Sweet Security api
for managing all Sweet configuration via IaC


## Example Usage

```terraform
terraform {
  required_providers {
    sweet = {
      source = "sweet-security/sweet"
    }
  }
}

provider "sweet" {
  api_key = "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
  secret = "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}
```
Obtain tenant api key & secret from [Sweet platform](https://app.sweet.security) inside settings -> API Tokens

